nessinsider.com%2Fmain-street-trump-trade-war-tariffs-small-businesses-impact-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrick-and-mortar%20retailers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20online%20small%20businesses%2C%20many%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20tariffs%20are%20forcing%20them%20to%20pass%20the%20cost%20to%20consumers%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20because%20they%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%20for%20smaller%20operations%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20same%20bargaining%20power%20with%20suppliers%20or%20cash%20flow%20as%20larger%20retailers%20like%20Walmart.%20Suppliers%20in%20some%20manufacturing%20hubs%20like%20China%20are%20also%20seeing%20ever%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-companies-china-suppliers-cut-prices-trump-tariff-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E-shrinking%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-companies-china-suppliers-cut-prices-trump-tariff-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20margins%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20absorb%20the%20tariff%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmall%20businesses%20are%20basically%20in%20danger%20of%20going%20out%20of%20business%20because%20of%20these%20high%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Peter%20Cohan%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20management%20at%20Babson%20College%20and%20a%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they're%20trying%20to%20preserve%20the%20trust%20of%20their%20customers%20by%20being%20very%20transparent%20about%20why%20they're%20raising%20the%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20they're%20going%20to%20lose%20customers%20because%20of%20the%20higher%20rates%2C%20but%20at%20least%20being%20transparent%20will%20help%20reduce%20the%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-effects-retailers-consumer-brands-hasbro-coca-cola-amazon-adidas-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%