ta-ablation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%2C%20suggests%20that%20Google's%20control%20of%20the%20search%20market%20may%20be%20lower%20than%20previously%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCombined%2C%20we%20estimate%20Google's%20search%20share%20is%20closer%20to%2065-70%25%20vs.%20the%2090%25%20we%20often%20hear%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222910825e-10cc-439a-8f93-1058ba469db2%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20slice%20of%20pie%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20insists%20that%20it's%20seeing%20more%20searches%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%202000s%2C%20the%20company%20has%20managed%20to%20harvest%20vast%20amounts%20of%20searches%20by%20paying%20Apple%20a%20fee%20to%20make%20its%20search%20engine%20the%20default%20on%20Apple's%20Safari%20web%20browser.%20As%20recently%20as%202022%2C%20Google%20had%20paid%20Apple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-iphone-search-engine-safari-deal-20-billion-2022-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20least%20%2420%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20massive%20fee%20that%20signals%20how%20much%20value%20Google%20sees%20in%20having%20Apple%20users%20turn%20to%20its%20search%20engine%20for%20all%20their%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20maintains%20that%20this%20partnership%20continues%20to%20drive%20growth%20in%20searches.%20Cue's%20comments%20were%20provocative%20enough%20to%20prompt%20the%20search%20giant%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fsearch%2Fstatement-press-reports-about-search-traffic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissue%20a%20public%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Boverall%20query%20growth%26quot%3B%20in%20Search%2C%20including%20an%20increase%20in%20total%20queries%20coming%20from%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20little%20doubt%20among%20industry%20watchers%20that%20the%20overall%20search%20pie%20is%20growing%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0though%20figures%20from%20research%20firm%20Statcounter%20suggest%20Google's%20control%20of%20the%20global%20search%20has%20fallen%20slightly.%20The%20big%20question%20is%20whether%20Google's%20slice%20of%20that%20pie%20is%20shrinking%20relative%20to%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgs.statcounter.com%2Fsearch-engine-market-share%23monthly-202206-202503%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStatcounter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google's%20share%20of%20global%20search%20traffic%20fell%20to%2089.71%25%20in%20March%202025%2C%20down%20from%20about%2091%25%20in%20March%202024%20and%20about%2093%25%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20competing%20search%20products%20are%20growing.%20In%20April%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20that%20around%2010%25%20of%20the%20world%20uses%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20would%20be%20at%20least%20800%20million%20users.%20Meta%20also%20said%20that%20about%201%20billion%20people%20use%20AI%20across%20its%20various%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20market%20expands%20with%20AI%20as%20chatbots%20and%20generative%20tools%20expand%20the%20definition%20of%20search.%20Google%20could%20reap%20the%20rewards%20here%2C%20though%20this%20also%20creates%20an%20opening%20for%20competitors%20charging%20as%20fast%20as%20possible%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20search%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20analysts%20estimated%20that%20generative%20AI%20queries%20that%20run%20through%20chatbots%20such%20as%20ChatGPT%20are%20reaching%20volumes%20close%20to%2015%25%20of%20the%20queries%20processed%20by%20Google%20and%20other%20traditional%20search%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f29842f8-d36a-43f6-8217-29aa69be9fd6%5C%22%3EAnalysts%20are%20split%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%20are%20divided%20on%20just%20how%20much%20of%20a%20threat%20Google's%20search%20business%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20longtime%20Apple%20analyst%20Ming-Chi%20Kuo%20took%20to%20X%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20explain%20why%20he%20felt%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20to%20think%20generative%20AI%20would%20not%20affect%20Google's%20advertising%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20growth%20of%20Google's%20advertising%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20hasn't%20had%20much%20competition%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenAI%20service%20providers%20have%20not%20launched%20advertising%20businesses%2C%20so%20Google%20Ads%20remains%20the%20best%20choice%20for%20online%20advertisers%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuo%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20following%20statement%20by%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20services%2C%20Eddy%20Cue%2C%20implies%20that%20Google%20search%20and%20advertising%20business%20are%20facing%20potential%20threats%20from%20generative%20AI%20(GenAI)%3A%3Cbr%3ECue%20noted%20that%20searches%20on%20Safari%20dipped%20for%20the%20first%20time%20last%20month%2C%20which%20he%20attributed%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20%E9%83%AD%E6%98%8E%E9%8C%A4%20(Ming-Chi%20Kuo)%20(%40mingchikuo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmingchikuo%2Fstatus%2F1920177692781261211%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKuo%20likened%20Google's%20situation%20to%20the%20one%20Yahoo%20faced%20during%20the%202000s.%20The%20company's%20advertising%20business%2C%20launched%20in%201995%2C%20only%20started%20declining%20in%202008%2C%20despite%20newfound%20competition%20from%20Google's%20AdWords%20business%20arriving%20back%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20investment%20bank%20Jefferies%20have%20a%20different%20view.%20In%20a%20research%20note%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20analysts%20had%20a%20particular%20word%20to%20describe%20the%20roughly%20%24155%20billion%20sell-off%20in%20Google's%20stock%20following%20Cue's%20comments%3A%20%26quot%3Boverblown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20acknowledged%20that%20Google's%20AI-powered%20%26quot%3BOverviews%26quot%3B%20feature%20may%20act%20as%20a%20headwind%20right%20now%20as%20it%20is%20resulting%20in%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20searches%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20Google%20will%20%26quot%3Bbe%20able%20to%20ramp%20monetization%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20AI%20summary%20feature%20over%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20don't%20see%20a%20scenario%20where%20Apple%20shifts%20away%20from%20Google%20and%20causes%20as%20much%20harm%20as%20investors%20might%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Safari%20is%20significant%2C%20it%20does%20not%20represent%20the%20entirety%20of%20search%20activity%3B%20iOS%20accounts%20for%2018%25%20of%20operating%20systems%2C%20and%20Safari%20holds%2017%25%20of%20the%20browser%20market%20share%20compared%20to%20Chrome's%2066%25%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20something%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20628-228-1836.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20articl