%20AI%20efforts%2C%20even%20when%20some%20of%20those%20efforts%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-glue-pizza-i-tried-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembarrassing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20later%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fsearch%2Fstatement-press-reports-about-search-traffic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20put%20out%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20basically%20said%20Cue%20was%20wrong%2C%20without%20actually%20saying%20that%20out%20loud.%20Instead%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20continuing%20to%20see%20increasing%20searches%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat%20includes%20an%20increase%20in%20total%20queries%20coming%20from%20Apple's%20devices%20and%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20%3Cem%3Elooks%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20two%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20and%20valuable%20companies%20are%20disagreeing%20over%20basic%2C%20knowable%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20people%20who%20pay%20attention%20to%20this%20stuff%20are%20focusing%20on%20three%20key%20words%20in%20Google's%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3Btotal%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bdevices%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bplatforms.%26quot%3B%20And%20the%20absence%20of%20another%20word%3A%20%26quot%3BSafari.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20leading%20them%20to%20translate%20Google's%20statement%20this%20way%3A%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20Apple%20really%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20seeing%20fewer%20searches%20on%20Safari%2C%20the%20default%20web%20browser%20on%20iPhones.%20But%20you%20can%20use%20Google%20in%20other%20ways%20on%20iPhones%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20via%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fgoogle%2Fid284815942%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20via%20Google's%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fgoogle-chrome%2Fid535886823%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChrome%20browser%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20people%20are%20using%20those%20more%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20counter%20any%20decline%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssuming%20that%20this%20translation%20is%20accurate%2C%20that%20should%20reassure%20Google%20and%20its%20boosters%20a%20bit%2C%20though%20not%20completely%3A%20Cue%20said%20the%20searches%20on%20Safari%20were%20down%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20signal%20you%20can%20just%20wave%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20Safari%20Google%20searchers%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20really%20moving%20to%20things%20like%20the%20Google%20app%20instead%2C%20that%20also%20underlines%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20who%20used%20to%20just%20type%20something%20into%20their%20iPhone%20browser%20know%20now%20they%20can%20get%20results%20other%20ways.%20And%20there's%20no%20reason%20they%20couldn't%20also%20be%20searching%20on%20Google%20competitors%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20rep%20declined%20to%20comment%3B%20Apple%20hasn't%20responded%20to%20my%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20investors%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20don't%20seem%20100%25%20convinced%20by%20Google's%20statement%3A%20The%20stock%20is%20up%203%25%20on%20Thursday%2C%20which%20means%20Google%20is%20still%20worth%205%25%20less%20than%20it%20was%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20when%20Cue%20started%20testifying%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20vs.%20Google%20antitrust%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20second%20question%20Google%20and%20Apple%20watchers%20are%20speculating%20about%3A%20Why%20did%20Cue%20say%20what%20he%20said%20in%20court%2C%20after%20all%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FOccam%2527s_razor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOccam's%20razor%3C%2Fa%3E%20guy%2C%20so%20my%20first%20take%20was%20that%20Cue%20answered%20the%20questions%20he%20was%20asked%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20also%20a%204D%20chess%20argument%2C%20put%20forth%20by%20folks%20like%20MoffettNathanson's%20analyst%20Michael%20Nathanson.%20It%20goes%20like%20this%3A%20Cue%20has%20an%20incentive%20to%20portray%20Google%20as%20a%20wounded%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-iphone-search-engine-safari-deal-20-billion-2022-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20pays%20Apple%20at%20least%20%2420%20billion%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20Google%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20Safari%20(that's%20the%20reason%20Cue%20has%20insight%20into%20Google's%20search%20activity)%2C%20and%20a%20federal%20judge%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-google-iphone-search-deal-antitrust-ruling-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20has%20an%20illegal%20monopoly%20in%20search%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20the%20remedies%20the%20judge%20could%20push%20for%20would%20be%20to%20prevent%20Google%20from%20paying%20Apple%20for%20that%20valuable%20real%20estate%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20mean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-apple-search-payments-iphone-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20could%20lose%20all%20of%20that%20high-margin%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20theory%20goes%2C%20convincing%20the%20judge%20that%20Google%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20stranglehold%20on%20search%2C%20because%20of%20AI%20competition%2C%20might%20allow%20those%20payments%20to%20keep%20flowing%