%2C%20and%20A5%20sizes%20for%20copier%20paper%20or%20sent%20for%20ruling%20and%20printing%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20notebooks%20and%20journals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20no%20bright%20white%20papers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20bleaching%20agents%20at%20all%2C%20which%20is%20why%20our%20paper%20is%20not%20bright%20white.%20At%20first%2C%20people%20questioned%20it.%20But%20now%2C%20they%20associate%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400838%2Fathangudi-tiles-chettinad-heritage-tamilnadu-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20tone%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20authenticity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashutosh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuality%20control%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20for%20the%20co-founders.%20At%20their%20in-house%20testing%20lab%2C%20each%20batch%20is%20tested%20for%20GSM%2C%20moisture%2C%20fibre%20strength%2C%20and%20uniformity.%20If%20any%20batch%20falls%20short%2C%20it%20is%20sent%20back%20for%20reprocessing.%20Once%20approved%2C%20the%20paper%20is%20shipped%20to%20their%20partnered%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20the%20final%20products%20are%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescript%20does%20not%20use%20any%20bleaching%20agents%20to%20make%20the%20papers%20white%20so%20they%20have%20the%20natural%20tone%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691.jpg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426227%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERescript%20does%20not%20use%20any%20bleaching%20agents%20to%20make%20the%20papers%20white%20so%20they%20have%20the%20natural%20tone%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20their%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%2C%20the%20paper%20also%20holds%20a%20Forest%20Stewardship%20Council%20(FSC)%20certification%2C%20which%20means%20it%20comes%20from%20responsibly%20managed%20forests%20that%20provide%20environmental%2C%20social%2C%20and%20economic%20benefits.%20It%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20trust%20that%20the%20products%20are%20not%20just%20high%20in%20quality%2C%20but%20also%20kind%20to%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20invested%20in%20binding%2C%20stitching%2C%20squaring%2C%20and%20spiral%20machines%20at%20our%20partner%20factory%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naren.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20Lineomatic%20machine%20for%20notebook%20production%2C%20but%20we%20have%20partnered%20with%20a%20vendor%20who%20does%2C%20and%20we%20have%20invested%20in%20essential%20machines%20so%20we%20can%20handle%20key%20parts%20of%20the%20process%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashutosh%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20big%20moves%20in%20a%20small%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20factory%2C%20the%20team%20begins%20by%20manually%20counting%20the%20sheets%20for%20each%20notebook.%20For%20instance%2C%20to%20make%20a%20160-page%20notebook%2C%20workers%20sort%20and%20layer%20the%20required%20number%20of%20sheets%2C%20placing%20separators%20in%20between.%20These%20stacks%20are%20then%20placed%20into%20a%20chain-link%20machine%2C%20along%20with%20the%20notebook%20cover%2C%20where%20the%20pages%20are%20pinned%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notebooks%20then%20move%20on%20to%20a%20squaring%20machine%2C%20which%20flattens%20and%20aligns%20the%20edges.%20After%20that%2C%20they%20are%20sent%20to%20a%20cutting%20machine%20to%20give%20the%20notebook%20a%20neat%20and%20finished%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournals%20follow%20a%20slightly%20different%20process.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20ruling%2C%20the%20pages%20are%20stitched%20rather%20than%20pinned%2C%20and%20then%20taken%20to%20a%20perfect%20binding%20machine.%20This%20machine%20uses%20hot%20glue%20to%20bind%20the%20stitched%20pages%20to%20a%20sturdy%20cover%2C%20giving%20the%20journal%20both%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341205%2Fbamboo-furniture-gujarat-professor-patented-chair-sustainable-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20and%20durability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20co-founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%